text: Altaac is a village and town in the Khizi Rayon of Azerbaijan. It is also known as Altiagach, Altyagach, Alty-Agatsch, Altiaghach, and Alyagach. 1,180 people live there. The municipality is made up of Altaac, Qzlqzma, isti Klyuc and Yarmca. == References == == Other websites == * Category:Settlements in Azerbaijan
